---
title: Chicken Milanese with Crispy Potatoes, Mixed Greens, and Creamy Lemon-Chive Dressing
description: Lemon and garlic are the perfect flavor duo in this crispy chicken Milanese. For a light yet hearty meal, we’re serving it alongside crispy roasted potatoes and a bright side salad.
